A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 2 of Chapter 70 of Title 36 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to service delivery, so as to require service delivery agreement to include a growth
3 boundary agreement component; to provide for circumstances when growth boundary
4 agreements may be excluded; to provide definitions; to provide for related matters; to
5 provide for an effective date; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Article 2 of Chapter 70 of Title 36 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
9 service delivery, is amended by revising Code Section 36-70-23, relating to required
10 components, as such Code section becomes effective on January 1, 2026, as follows:
11 "36-70-23.
12 Each local government service delivery strategy shall include the following components:
13 (1) An identification of all local government services presently provided or primarily
14 funded by each general purpose local government and each authority within the county,
15 or providing services within the county, and a description of the geographic area in which
16 the identified services are provided by each jurisdiction;
